      "updated": 1777239727
    },
    {
      "id": "69ee86ae0000000000105a15",
      "text": "\t[reaction people to body control #hardstyle #dj #calisthenics #reaction #gym #motivation #aura - YouTube https://www.youtube.com/shorts/C-kR0y4JkHU]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1777239727,
      "updated": 1777239727
    },
    {
      "id": "69ee86af0000000000105a17",
      "text": "\t\tこれ好き",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1777239727,
      "updated": 1777239729
    },
    {
      "id": "69ee86b00000000000105a18",
      "text": "\t\tわかるわぁ、身体能力で周囲をわからせる快感",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1777239729,
      "updated": 1777239742
    },
    {
      "id": "69ee873c0000000000105a1b",
      "text": "\t\t\t僕はゲーセンの音ゲーでこれをやってる",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1777239869,
      "updated": 1777239876
    },
    {
      "id": "69ee87510000000000105a1c",
      "text": "\t\t\tただ見た目がわかりやすくないと通じないんだよなぁ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1777239889,
      "updated": 1777239902
    },
    {
      "id": "69ee86bd0000000000105a19",
      "text": "\t\tフラッグ、ドラゴンフラッグ、マッスルアップ（懸垂から上がるやつでパルクール技）、片手逆立ちみたいなのはわからんけどブレイクダンスでカバーできる、逆立ち腕立て",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1777239742,
      "updated": 1777239802
    },
    {
      "id": "69ee87180000000000105a1a",
      "text": "\t\tあと上水平（プランシェ）もできるとかっこいい、この人ならすぐできそう",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1777239832,
      "updated": 1777240021
    },
