    {
      "id": "69eecdf00000000000e4b810",
      "text": "[hoagecko.icon]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777257967,
      "updated": 1777257968
    },
    {
      "id": "69eecebf00000000000673da",
      "text": " [Scrapboxの未解決問題#60861be11280f0000072ce9f]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777258174,
      "updated": 1777259559
    },
    {
      "id": "69eed42a0000000000e4b812",
      "text": " \t[Wayback Machine]に保存できないなら個人のProjectはやめよう…",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777259561,
      "updated": 1777259588
    },
    {
      "id": "69eed4450000000000e4b813",
      "text": " \tと思っていたら普通に保存されていた",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777259588,
      "updated": 1777259596
    },
    {
      "id": "69eed44d0000000000e4b814",
      "text": " \t\t[https://web.archive.org/web/20251018224759/https://scrapbox.io/villagepump/%E4%BA%95%E6%88%B8%E7%AB%AF 井戸端 - 井戸端]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777259597,
      "updated": 1777259607
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef2e310000000000e70abf",
      "text": " \tそんなわけでやめるのは撤回する",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777282610,
      "updated": 1777289931
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef2f000000000000e70ac0",
      "text": " \t\tまあそもそも最近触っていないが",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777282817,
      "updated": 1777289935
    },
    {
      "id": "69eed52c0000000000e4b815",
      "text": " ✂ [シネクドキによる誤用]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777259819,
      "updated": 1777719632
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5adf30000000000cb94d4",
      "text": " ✂ [根気強い対話―2026/04/27]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777708532,
      "updated": 1777719641
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef4b4300000000000409b7",
      "text": " [知の機能的な最適化と解釈や尊厳の代替不可能性に関する議論]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1777290052,
      "updated": 1777292540
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef4b4900000000000409b8",
      "text": " \tこれ[Posfie] (旧[Togetter])でまとめた方がよさそう",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777290058,
      "updated": 1777290080
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef4b6000000000000409b9",
      "text": " \t\t著作権を考えるとここまで全文を転載するのは不味いと思います",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777290081,
      "updated": 1777290206
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef504600000000008bfd45",
      "text": " \tご指摘ありがとうございます。削除しました[terang.icon]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1777291335,
      "updated": 1777291343
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef504f00000000008bfd46",
      "text": " \t\tcf. [2026/04/27#69ef4d3900000000000c52a4]",
