    {
      "id": "69eeda080000000000a31f6d",
      "text": " 同人誌描き終わった！はれるや〜〜〜！！",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1777261064,
      "updated": 1777261079
    },
    {
      "id": "69eee0a700000000006af98c",
      "text": " \t🎉[Hiro Aki.icon][hoagecko.icon][atohs.icon][koyoshi.icon][vlzs.icon][sta.icon][taktamur.icon][mtane0412.icon][基素.icon][terang.icon][takker.icon][nomadoor.icon][seibe.icon][hoshihara.icon][imo.icon]",
      "userId": "5ad57975d54cd50014068484",
      "created": 1777262760,
      "updated": 1777299285
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeda170000000000a31f6e",
      "text": " 超好きな同人作家さん、ここ数ヶ月沈黙していたが私が出るのと同じイベントで新刊を出す模様で最高",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1777261080,
      "updated": 1777261139
    },
    {
      "id": "69eedbe80000000000a31f70",
      "text": " [パロタ]食べたい",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1777261545,
      "updated": 1777261558
    },
    {
      "id": "69eee3bb0000000000a31f75",
      "text": "  [https://gyazo.com/87916254ac1bee4410069a57505f12b5]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1777263547,
      "updated": 1777263564
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeecf40000000000d3877d",
      "text": "  ナンですかこれは……[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777265908,
      "updated": 1777265933
    },
    {
      "id": "69eefb710000000000f83b3a",
      "text": "   ナンでしょうね…[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1777269617,
      "updated": 1777269624
    },
    {
      "id": "69eefb780000000000f83b3b",
      "text": "    いいえ、parottaです [/icons/slowparrot.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1777269625,
      "updated": 1777269649
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef44b000000000004d4b1a",
      "text": "  食べたーーい[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1777288369,
      "updated": 1777288374
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef449e00000000004d4b19",
      "text": "  ジャポニカ米？なのかな[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1777288351,
      "updated": 1777288364
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef49b60000000000646c8d",
      "text": "   ジャポニカ米だった、インド米追加料金であるみたい[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1777289654,
      "updated": 1777289680
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef6f6c0000000000f2abac",
      "text": "  うまそ[imo.icon]",
      "userId": "5ad57975d54cd50014068484",
      "created": 1777299310,
      "updated": 1777299312
    },
    {
      "id": "69eee31b0000000000a31f72",
      "text": " フォークとナイフの文化圏の人、キャベツの千切りサラダが出てきた時どうするんやろ…としばらく考え、たぶんナイフでフォークの背に乗せて食べるのかな…となった",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1777263390,
      "updated": 1777263435
    },
    {
      "id": "69eee34f0000000000a31f73",
      "text": "  フォークですくっちゃいけない縛り厳しくない？",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1777263440,
      "updated": 1777263459
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef0df600000000007f3709",
      "text": " [Liquid Glass]あんまり好きじゃないんだけど、そもそもこういう水とかガラスっぽい見た目が好きじゃないかも、メタルっぽい感じが好き",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1777274358,
      "updated": 1777274410
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef0e3300000000007f370a",
      "text": "  久しぶりにiphoneのケース外して背面ガラス見て思った",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1777274420,
      "updated": 1777274441
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef61310000000000f83b43",
      "text": " 白菜を切ってたらめっちゃ虫だらけでアーとなったが途中でどうせゆでちゃえばたんぱく質だしなと思ってどうでもよくなった",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1777295666,
      "updated": 1777295709
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef642b0000000000624904",
      "text": " \tたくましい精神で良い[Hiro Aki.icon]",
      "userId": "65e1289acd012200235729c0",
      "created": 1777296430,
      "updated": 1777296462
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef738f0000000000543dac",
      "text": " \t昨日、走ってる途中で口の中に虫が入ってきてこれになりました[atohs.icon]",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1777300368,
      "updated": 1777300382
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef81a50000000000180483",
      "text": " \t チャリで走ってるときたまにある、嫌[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1777303974,
      "updated": 1777303999
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef81c10000000000180484",
      "text": " \tとはいえちょっと気になるので調べたら[ハクサイダニ]というやつらしい",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1777304001,
      "updated": 1777304019
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef81f00000000000180485",
      "text": " \t ハダニの仲間だろうか、おおむね水で流したのでまあいいか",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1777304049,
      "updated": 1777304069
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef73b400000000009dd6b0",
      "text": " [皆様ありがとう。助かりました―2026/04/27]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777300404,
      "updated": 1777720444
    },
    {
      "id": "69eff0c500000000001d32a4",
      "text": " なんと、次の同人誌を今日から書きます",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1777332422,
      "updated": 1777332422
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef783700000000001cac7e",
      "text": "  ストイックすぎる",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1777301560,
      "updated": 1777301562
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef7a1c0000000000543dbf",
      "text": "  あまりにもえらすぎる……[atohs.icon]",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1777302045,
      "updated": 1777302070
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef7a2b0000000000543dc0",
      "text": "  \t真似します",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1777302060,
      "updated": 1777302062
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef7fa70000000000180481",
      "text": "  \tがんばりましょう…🤝[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1777303464,
      "updated": 1777303486
    },
    {
      "id": "69efc1f50000000000728961",
      "text": "  背中が見えない[基素.icon]",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1777320437,
      "updated": 1777320449
    },
    {
      "id": "69eee6e50000000000b7331f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1777264357,
      "updated": 1777264357
    },
    {
      "id": "69eee6e50000000000b73320",
      "text": "[terang.icon]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1777264357,
      "updated": 1777264359
    },
    {
      "id": "69eee6e80000000000b73321",
      "text": "\tとめ。はね。はしゃぎ。",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1777264360,
      "updated": 1777264388
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef387500000000002372d3",
      "text": "\t数日前から目に入っていた[X.icon]上の、大学でのAIチューターの是非の議論が、枝分かれリプライとコメ付きRPで、流れが大変追いづらくなってて辛い",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1777285238,
      "updated": 1777285475
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef38c500000000002372d5",
      "text": "\t\ttogetter/posfile探したがない様子。",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1777285317,
      "updated": 1777285327
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef38b600000000002372d4",
      "text": "\t\tちょっと自分用にまとめるかな。",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1777285303,
      "updated": 1777285306
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef3fab00000000002372d8",
      "text": "\t\t[- まとめてみた: 知の機能的な最適化と解釈や尊厳の代替不可能性に関する議論]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1777287084,
      "updated": 1777290596
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef3faf00000000002372d9",
      "text": "\t\t[/komoji-od/Deep Researchは〈専門〉を脱せない]の話と関連しそうで興味を持った",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1777287088,
      "updated": 1777287525
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef4d3400000000000c52a3",
      "text": "\t\tvia. [2026/04/27#69ef4b4300000000000409b7]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1777290548,
      "updated": 1777290553
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef4d3900000000000c52a4",
      "text": "\t\t\t私は私の判断で著作権法上ないしはX利用規約上問題ないかと考えての記載でしたがグレーであることは認めるので削除することにします。",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1777290553,
      "updated": 1777291308
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef4f8e0000000000d443b7",
      "text": "\t\t自分が象徴的だと感じたポストだけ置いておきます。",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1777291151,
      "updated": 1777291161
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef4f980000000000d443b8",
      "text": "\t\t>[https://x.com/motoakihara/status/2048338027811135673 @motoakihara]: レオ・シュピッツァーの名を出すまでもなく、「読む」という行為は非常に人間的（ヒューマニティ―）なものです。そもそも詩を読むという行為はその中でも、おそらくちょっと特殊です。ですので、学生諸君のまえで先行する者として、少なくとも私（たち）にはそれを実際に行う必要があります。（続く）",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1777291161,
      "updated": 1777291163
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef629c000000000012cd09",
      "text": "\t\tなお上のポスト者の相手方の主張は、今まさに[消したいページを挙げてく]でなされている話と地続きだと思っている。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777296033,
      "updated": 1777296079
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef39f500000000002372d6",
      "text": "\t上の議論の公教育に関することは、16年前の[https://posfie.com/@katokiti2003/p/ZmFdH0W 2010/11/02　芦田先生と西川先生のやりとり - posfie]を思い出す",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1777285621,
      "updated": 1777288672
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef39fc00000000002372d7",
      "text": "\t\t専門家（らしき）人同士の会話",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1777285628,
      "updated": 1777285658
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef62d1000000000012cd0a",
      "text": "\t[100分de名著ウィトゲンシュタイン] 最終回 待機。",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1777296081,
      "updated": 1777296097
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef822a0000000000bdbab5",
      "text": "\t\t視聴終了。",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1777304107,
      "updated": 1777304112
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef76d10000000000a4a904",
      "text": "\t\t今回のテーマは「心を持つことの条件」",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1777301202,
      "updated": 1777301214
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef76dd0000000000a4a905",
      "text": "\t\t[ウィトゲンシュタイン.icon]心には「予見できないもの」が大きな役割を果たしていると考えた。",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1777301214,
      "updated": 1777301258
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef77180000000000a4a906",
      "text": "\t\t\tそれをどこで経験するかというと、他の誰かとの関係、つまり[言語ゲーム]によって経験する。",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1777301273,
      "updated": 1777301282
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef77240000000000a4a907",
      "text": "\t\t\t人間は元来予測したい。そのためにあらゆる予見をする。そして同時にそれが裏切られる。",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1777301285,
      "updated": 1777301299
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef77500000000000a4a908",
      "text": "\t\t\t人間の心は、他者とのままならないコミュニケーションの中に立ち現れるもの",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1777301329,
      "updated": 1777301340
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef70030000000000c7431a",
      "text": "\t今日新しく知った語: [ギュられる], [ギュ鳴らし]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1777299459,
      "updated": 1777299666
    },
    {
      "id": "69eedc1d1280f000000039d3f9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1777261597,
      "updated": 1777261597
    },
    {
      "id": "69eee9920000000000649845",
      "text": "[hoshihara.icon]",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1777265041,
      "updated": 1777265042
    },
    {
      "id": "69eee9930000000000649847",
      "text": " あー",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1777265042,
      "updated": 1777265045
    },
    {
      "id": "69eef6150000000000f83b37",
      "text": "  まー[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1777268246,
      "updated": 1777268248
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef08c60000000000c097c9",
      "text": "   いー[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1777273030,
      "updated": 1777273032
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef0cb300000000006637c5",
      "text": "   \tろー[terang.icon]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1777274035,
      "updated": 1777274040
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef0d4d00000000008fbdd2",
      "text": "   \t\tのー[atohs.icon]",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1777274189,
      "updated": 1777274192
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef1377000000000020e08b",
      "text": "   \t\t かー[vlzs.icon]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777275767,
      "updated": 1777275769
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef16aa0000000000d387d2",
      "text": "   \t\t \tしー[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777276586,
      "updated": 1777276591
    },
    {
      "id": "69eef41b00000000008fbdca",
      "text": "\t↑アイコンが並んでカラフルになっておりかわいい",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1777267740,
      "updated": 1777289631
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5da3d000000000013345d",
      "text": "\t\t↑カラフルと↓眼精疲労の温度差で風邪ひきそう[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777719870,
      "updated": 1777719892
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef4d160000000000bb7a86",
      "text": "\t[眼精疲労がひどすぎて目が痛くて開けるのがつらい。]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777290517,
      "updated": 1777719936
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef49510000000000bb7a85",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1777289553,
      "updated": 1777289553
    },
    {
      "id": "69eef41b00000000008fbdcb",
      "text": "[atohs.icon]",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1777267740,
      "updated": 1777267741
    },
    {
      "id": "69eef41d00000000008fbdcc",
      "text": "　入稿！入稿！入稿！入稿！！！！！！！",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1777267741,
      "updated": 1777267752
    },
    {
      "id": "69eef42700000000008fbdcd",
      "text": "　入稿したので出るはず！！！！",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1777267752,
      "updated": 1777267759
    },
    {
      "id": "69eef42f00000000008fbdce",
      "text": "　\t[https://gyazo.com/f010c96b492500b2196b03f187365783]",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1777267759,
      "updated": 1777267768
    },
    {
      "id": "69eef43800000000008fbdcf",
      "text": "\t\t[**********-() [めでたい.icon]][Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777267768,
      "updated": 1777281905
    },
    {
      "id": "69eef6320000000000f83b38",
      "text": "\t\tめでたい[caki.icon][suto3.icon][mtane0412.icon][koyoshi.icon][vlzs.icon][sta.icon][taktamur.icon][takker.icon][基素.icon][terang.icon][Hiro Aki.icon][hoagecko.icon][nomadoor.icon][hoshihara.icon][seibe.icon][imo.icon]",
      "userId": "5ad57975d54cd50014068484",
      "created": 1777268275,
      "updated": 1777299206
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef0dad00000000008fbdd3",
      "text": "\t[誤用としての提喩]という発想あまり無かったな。集めると面白そう",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777274286,
      "updated": 1777284999
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef0dc800000000008fbdd5",
      "text": "\t\tロボットのこと全部ガンダム系だと、ゲームのことみんなファミコンとかがありそう",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1777274312,
      "updated": 1777274329
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef0dd800000000008fbdd6",
      "text": "\tGA4のBigQuery連携って無料でどこまで使えるか気になるドラゴン",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1777274329,
      "updated": 1777275987
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef145300000000008fbdd8",
      "text": "\t今月はCursorくんのトークンが上限いきそうなので、つなぎでClaudeの無料プラン使ってみるか",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1777275988,
      "updated": 1777276499
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef165300000000008fbdda",
      "text": "\t\tVS Codeで使うにはProプランが必要だな",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1777276499,
      "updated": 1777276522
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef151d00000000008fbdd9",
      "text": "\tCursorってオンデマンド課金にした方が経済的のように思うんだけど、最初から$60課金するメリットってあるんだろうか",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1777276189,
      "updated": 1777276217
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef166000000000008fbddb",
      "text": "\t✂ [Cosenseプロジェクトにおける固有名詞の取り扱いってかなり難しそうだ]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777276513,
      "updated": 1777720004
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef777d0000000000543dbb",
      "text": " そういえば、井戸端の存在をはじめて認知したのって、Google検索で[Scrapboxの収益化]が上の方に表示されたからだということを急に思い出した",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1777301373,
      "updated": 1777301412
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef77e30000000000543dbc",
      "text": " 今日行った文房具屋ではじめて[測量野帳]というものを見つけたので買ってみたが、特に使う予定がないな",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1777301475,
      "updated": 1777301505
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef76bb00000000009dd6ba",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777301180,
      "updated": 1777301180
    },
    {
      "id": "69eefe680000000000e1b8b9",
      "text": "[mtane0412.icon]",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1777270376,
      "updated": 1777270378
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef08cf0000000000c097ca",
      "text": " なー",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1777273039,
      "updated": 1777274230
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef0e6800000000007f370b",
      "text": "  がー[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1777274472,
      "updated": 1777274477
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef14fb00000000001fa091",
      "text": "  \tくー[terang.icon]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1777276156,
      "updated": 1777276159
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef1649000000000020e0a4",
      "text": "  \t てー[vlzs.icon]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777276490,
      "updated": 1777276491
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef334c0000000000980a7c",
      "text": "  \t  みー[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1777283917,
      "updated": 1777283921
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef79a200000000009dd6c5",
      "text": "   \t  りー[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777301923,
      "updated": 1777301935
    },
    {
      "id": "69efed770000000000ca5117",
      "text": "   \t   んー[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1777331575,
      "updated": 1777331580
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef0d730000000000a81b17",
      "text": " create-next-appで`This is NOT the Next.js you know`というAGENTS.mdが作られるようになってる？",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1777274227,
      "updated": 1777276595
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef4cbb0000000000ce48fa",
      "text": " ゆーいちさんの新作Strummo",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1777290428,
      "updated": 1777290490
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef4cc20000000000ce48fb",
      "text": "  [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6SgkOFFD1yA]",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1777290435,
      "updated": 1777290435
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef5eef000000000082fde4",
      "text": "  Instachordは値上げ、安い価格帯に新作を投入する",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1777295088,
      "updated": 1777295117
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef5f07000000000082fde5",
      "text": "   ただの廉価版じゃなくて新コンセンプトで作るっぽい",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1777295117,
      "updated": 1777295120
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef4cc30000000000ce48fc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1777290435,
      "updated": 1777290435
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef168d000000000058029d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1777276557,
      "updated": 1777276557
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef08cf0000000000c097cb",
      "text": "[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1777273039,
      "updated": 1777273039
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef08d00000000000c097cc",
      "text": " 寝不足なのか酷く眠くて頭が動かない",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1777273039,
      "updated": 1777273053
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef08de0000000000c097cd",
      "text": " 　課題にも取り組めなさそう",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1777273053,
      "updated": 1777273060
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef08e40000000000c097ce",
      "text": " 眠気覚ましにボルダーしてみたが、あまり眠気はさめなかった",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1777273060,
      "updated": 1777273090
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef09020000000000c097d0",
      "text": " 　体を動かしても眠い",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1777273090,
      "updated": 1777273093
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef09060000000000c097d1",
      "text": " 　30分くらいで切り上げた",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1777273093,
      "updated": 1777273102
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef090f0000000000c097d2",
      "text": " ただ、体育館を行ったり来たり動いているうちに、少しだけマシになったかも",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1777273102,
      "updated": 1777273125
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef09260000000000c097d3",
      "text": " デカビタCを買って飲んだ",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1777273125,
      "updated": 1777273141
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef09350000000000c097d5",
      "text": " 　さらに少しマシになったかも",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1777273141,
      "updated": 1777273148
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef093d0000000000c097d6",
      "text": " 今日は授業終わったらすぐ帰って寝よう",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1777273148,
      "updated": 1777273156
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef0c7a0000000000cc0200",
      "text": "  良き眠りを[taktamur.icon][imo.icon]",
      "userId": "5ad57975d54cd50014068484",
      "created": 1777273979,
      "updated": 1777299021
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef335c0000000000980a7d",
      "text": "  ねるぞー[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1777283933,
      "updated": 1777283947
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef339a000000000046fcbb",
      "text": " 自分のモバイル通信契約が5Gに対応していたことにようやく気づいた",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1777283995,
      "updated": 1777284023
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef33b6000000000046fcbc",
      "text": "  有効にした",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1777284023,
      "updated": 1777284030
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef45d30000000000fbd47e",
      "text": "  5G対応端末買った後、5G電波捕まえたり捕まえなかったりでバチクソ不安定になったので無効にしたの思い出した[Hiro Aki.icon]",
      "userId": "65e1289acd012200235729c0",
      "created": 1777288662,
      "updated": 1777288693
    },
    {
      "id": "69eefe680000000000e1b8ba",
      "text": "\t\tデフォルトでオフになっている場合があるのか。自分は勝手に5Gになっていた[imo.icon]",
      "userId": "5ad57975d54cd50014068484",
      "created": 1777270376,
      "updated": 1777299025
    },
    {
      "id": "69efed850000000000ca5118",
      "text": "\t\t3年間くらいOFFのままだった[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1777331589,
      "updated": 1777331620
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef6e320000000000f2abab",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ad57975d54cd50014068484",
      "created": 1777298996,
      "updated": 1777298996
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef0b1d000000000038ed82",
      "text": "[基素.icon]",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1777273630,
      "updated": 1777273631
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef0b20000000000038ed85",
      "text": " 春物着る季節すぐ終わる。夏は暑くてジメジメしてるから好きじゃないのにウェイトが上がってていやだな〜。",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1777273633,
      "updated": 1777273700
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef0dec00000000007f3708",
      "text": "  やだ〜[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1777274349,
      "updated": 1777274353
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef370400000000005be73e",
      "text": "  お気に入りの春ジャケットを着るタイミングが本当に無い…[nomadoor.icon]",
      "userId": "5f0ae250e8cd56001ee2dacc",
      "created": 1777284901,
      "updated": 1777284940
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef0b1e000000000038ed83",
      "text": " [日本の夏42年で3週間長く、春秋は短く「二季化」進む 三重大学研究 - 日本経済新聞 https://www.nikkei.com/article/DGXZQOUD112D70R11C25A0000000/]",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1777273630,
      "updated": 1777273738
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef0b1e000000000038ed84",
      "text": "  >2023年の夏の日数は6月11日〜10月9日の121日間だった。",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1777273630,
      "updated": 1777273806
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef0b8d000000000038ed86",
      "text": "  1/3夏じゃん",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1777273742,
      "updated": 1777273919
    },
